description: Summons a powerful Spirit Bear that can equip items
Causes the nearby enemies to flee
Morphs To Himself into a raging bear
Severs health from target and user
Transforms a creep into a creature

Creates a powerful of arcane energy

Draws mystical energies from the earth

Fires a long range with precision
Teleports Io to a different place
Changes form to match the targeted enemy
